com.sun.jts.jtsxa

Class XID

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.jts.jtsxa.XID
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Xid

    public class XID
extends Object
implements Xid
    The XID class provides an implementation of the X/Open transaction identifier it implements the javax.transaction.xa.Xid interface.
